# Hoggar

Hoggar is a personal R package for streamlining data analysis, including an RStudio project template with necessary folder structure and code starters.

## Installation

To install the `Hoggar` package, run the following code in R:

```{r}
if (!require(devtools)) install.packages("devtools")
devtools::install_github("slokmanex/Hoggar")
```

## Usage

Once you have installed `Hoggar`, you can find Hoggar as prat of project templates.

